BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 236.88 750 Td (HOW TO USE CHATGPT) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 50 740 m 562 740 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 715 Td (WHAT IS CHATGPT?) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 700 Td (ChatGPT is a free AI assistant you can talk to by typing. Think of) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 685 Td (it like texting a very knowledgeable friend who is available 24/7.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 670 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 655 Td (HOW TO GET STARTED:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 640 Td (1. Go to chat.openai.com on your computer or phone) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 625 Td (2. Create a free account \(just need an email address\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 610 Td (3. You will see a text box - that is where you type your 'prompt') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 595 Td (4. Type your question or request and press Enter) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 580 Td (5. ChatGPT will respond in seconds!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 565 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 550 Td (TIPS FOR BEST RESULTS:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 535 Td (- Be specific: 'Give me a recipe for chicken soup' works better) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 520 Td (  than just 'food ideas') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 505 Td (- Give context: 'I have diabetes' helps it tailor health advice) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 490 Td (- Ask follow-ups: Say 'Make it simpler' or 'Give me more detail') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 475 Td (- It is a conversation: You can keep asking questions) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 460 Td (- Copy and paste: You can copy prompts from this book directly) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 445 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 430 Td (IMPORTANT REMINDERS:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 415 Td (- ChatGPT can make mistakes - always verify important information) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 400 Td (- Never share passwords, Social Security numbers, or bank info) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 385 Td (- It is not a doctor - use health info as a starting point only) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 370 Td (- It cannot access the internet in real-time \(no current news\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 355 Td (- You can start a new conversation anytime) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 340 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 325 Td (HOW TO USE THIS BOOK:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 310 Td (Each prompt is written in BOLD - type it exactly as shown.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 295 Td ('Why this helps' explains what you will get back.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 280 Td ('My result' space is for you to write notes about what worked.) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
